3.1 Loading Forge
=================

Loading Magit doesn’t cause Forge to be loaded automatically.  Adding
something like this to your init file takes care of that:

     (with-eval-after-load 'magit
       (require 'forge))

Or if you use ‘use-package’:

     (use-package forge
       :after magit)


